Title: INTERIOR PANELS / TRIM: LOWER INSTRUMENT PANEL: REASSEMBLY; 2018 - 2019 MY Prius [11/2017 - 08/2019]

REASSEMBLY

PROCEDURE

1. INSTALL LOWER INSTRUMENT PANEL SUB-ASSEMBLY (except 11.6 Inch Display)

(a) Engage the guide and 4 clips.

(b) Install the lower instrument panel sub-assembly with the 7 screws <E>.

2. INSTALL LOWER INSTRUMENT PANEL SUB-ASSEMBLY (for 11.6 Inch Display)

(a) Engage the guide and 4 clips.

(b) Install the lower instrument panel sub-assembly with the 5 screws <E>.

3. INSTALL LOWER CENTER INSTRUMENT PANEL (for 11.6 Inch Display)

(a) Install the lower center instrument panel with the 8 screws <E>.

4. INSTALL LOWER INSTRUMENT COVER SUB-ASSEMBLY

(a) Install the lower instrument cover sub-assembly with the 4 screws <E>.

5. INSTALL ANTENNA CORD SUB-ASSEMBLY

Click here

6. INSTALL NO. 3 KNEE PROTECTOR BRACKET

(a) Install the No. 3 knee protector bracket with the 2 screws <E>.

7. INSTALL NO. 2 KNEE PROTECTOR BRACKET

(a) Install the No. 2 knee protector bracket with the 2 screws <E>.

8. INSTALL NO. 2 HEATER TO REGISTER DUCT (except 11.6 Inch Display)

(a) Install the No. 2 heater to register duct with the 2 screws <E> or <F>.

9. INSTALL NO. 2 HEATER TO REGISTER DUCT (for 11.6 Inch Display)

(a) Install the No. 2 heater to register duct with the 2 screws <E> or <F>.

10. INSTALL NO. 2 HEATER TO REGISTER DUCT SUB-ASSEMBLY

(a) Install the No. 2 heater to register duct sub-assembly with the 4 screws <E> or <F>.

11. INSTALL NO. 1 HEATER TO REGISTER DUCT SUB-ASSEMBLY

(a) Install the No. 1 heater to register duct sub-assembly with the 4 screws <E> or <F>.

12. INSTALL INSTRUMENT PANEL PASSENGER AIRBAG ASSEMBLY
